snippet.title: Kinniku Banzuke Vol. 1 (Psone JPN) - Gameplay
snippet.description:
Full Title: Kinniku Banzuke Vol.1: Oregasaikyouno Otokoda!

Also Known as Muscle Ranking. This is a collection of mini games from Konami based on a TV show.

The Tv show is currently airing as Unbeatable Banzuke on the G4 Network in the US. 

Here are just a few of the mini games included. I tried to show what success and failure look like. Daruma, Monster Box and Shot Gun Touch are shown in this video. The other mini games available on the disc are Kick Target, Brain Panic, Struck Out, The Tug of War and Hustler
